Title: iPhoneTracker for Windows and more
Description: iPhoneTracker is app for visualizing iPhone's user location data(i.e. the consolidated.db file), and this project is a Silverlight ported app, it can be use on Windows and any other platforms installed with Silverlight.
HomeWiki:
iPhoneTracker is app for visualizing iPhone's user location data(i.e. the consolidated.db file), and this project is a Silverlight ported app, it can be use on Windows and any other platforms installed with Silverlight.

This app utilized Out-of-browser capability of Silverlight, therefore it requires latest version of Silverlight to be installed.
